sentences.english: Concreting technology for the box girders and construction method for the prestressing system are dealt with as well.
sentences.chinese: 並介紹了箱梁混凝土的澆注工藝及預應力施工的方法。

sentences.english: This paper introduces the construction of precast yard, and expounds the equipment matching technology for the precast of single box-beam.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了預製廠建設，敘述了單箱梁預製設備配套技術。

sentences.english: Full use of stents in-situ box girder erection, heap pressure on the overall pre-cast-in-place.
sentences.chinese: 現澆箱梁採用滿堂支架架設，堆載預壓整體現澆。

sentences.english: A great amount of post tensioned pre-stressing concrete single box beam for double track (as called the Box Beam hereinafter) has been used on the line.
sentences.chinese: 該線大量採用後張法預應力混凝土雙線單箱簡支箱梁。

sentences.english: The paper mainly analyses the prestressed steel box girder.
sentences.chinese: 本文主要對預應力鋼箱梁進行了振動理論分析。

sentences.english: A two-span continuous curved box girder model was made with Perspex.
sentences.chinese: 建立一兩跨連續曲線箱梁有機玻璃試驗模型。

sentences.english: Open bottoms of steel box beams shall be protected by removable expanded metal mesh.
sentences.chinese: 鋼製箱梁的開放式底部應用活動金屬網進行保護。

sentences.english: The paper introduce one kind of external formwork system design of cast-in-place continuous box beam.
sentences.chinese: 本文介紹了一種現澆連續箱梁外模系統的設計。

sentences.english: Lateral internal force calculation of box girder still lacks accurate effective and simple method.
sentences.chinese: 箱梁橫向內力的計算目前還缺乏精確有效的簡化方法。

sentences.english: This paper has introduced how to use the graph theory method to calculate the sectorial coordinate of the variable cross-section box girder.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了用圖論法計算變截面箱梁斷面的扇性座標。

sentences.english: Erect support on box girder perform segmented concreting of bridge tower.
sentences.chinese: 在箱梁上搭設支架，分段澆築橋塔混凝土。

sentences.english: So this method has made the complex problem about the calculation of the box girder torsion much simpler.
sentences.chinese: 它使複雜的箱梁扭轉計算問題得到簡化。

sentences.english: The beams are used to support the whole structure during shifting of the brackets.
sentences.chinese: 箱梁用來在移動牛腿時支撐整個結構。

sentences.english: Cast-in-place box Liang uses the full house support to erect, piles carries the precompression overall cast-in-place.
sentences.chinese: 現澆箱梁採用滿堂支架架設，堆載預壓整體現澆。

sentences.english: The multichambered Thin-walled box girder hyperstatic unknown shearing flow calculated matrix equation is set up.
sentences.chinese: 建立了多室薄壁箱梁超靜定未知剪力計算矩陣方程。

sentences.english: Steel box girder is widely used in modern long-span suspension bridge structure.
sentences.chinese: 鋼箱梁結構在現代大跨度懸索橋體系中較多采用。

definition: to construct by hoisting ready-built components into place
to join the two sections (of a linear structure: bridge, dike etc) to complete its construction
